---

### [choco://intel-npu-driver](choco://intel-npu-driver/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)


---

This download installs Intel® NPU Driver - Windows* xx.x.xxx.xxxx for Intel® Core™ Ultra processors.

Intel ® NPU Driver for Windows* (Intel ® AI Boost) includes support for OpenVino™ 2025.2

